column1: # Isotopic fractionation factor summary data to accompany: Carbon isotopic fractionation in organic matter production consistent with benthic community composition across a coral reef flat
# Contact the corresponding author David A. Koweek with any questions (dkoweek@carnegiescience.edu)
# e_caco3 = Assumed isotopic fractionation factor for net calcification (per mil) for which e_om estimates are made
# min = Minimum e_om estimate for corresponding zone and e_caco3 value from bootstrap (per mil)
# quartile1 = 25% percentile of e_om estimate for corresponding zone and e_caco3 value from bootstrap (per mil)
# mean = Mean e_om estimate for corresponding zone and e_caco3 value from bootstrap (per mil)
# median = Median e_om estimate for corresponding zone and e_caco3 value from bootstrap (per mil)
# quartile3 = 75% percentile of e_om estimate for corresponding zone and e_caco3 value from bootstrap (per mil)
# max = Maximum e_om estimate for corresponding zone and e_caco3 value from bootstrap (per mil)
